Tristin Mays https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tristin_Mays 0 Tristin Mays (born June 10, 1990) is an American actress and singer. Mays currently stars in the reboot of the MacGyver series on CBS. She plays the character Riley Davis, who works as a covert operative for Matilda "Matty" Webber (Meredith Eaton) of the Phoenix Foundation.
